## AI Default Patterns (AVOID THESE!)

```
DON'T:
- Tailwind default colors (blue-500, gray-100)
- rounded-lg everywhere
- shadow-md on everything
- Centered hero + 3 feature cards layout
- Generic gradient: from-blue-500 to-purple-500
- System font stack without character
```

