## 5. Custom Cursor

```css
.custom-cursor { cursor: none; }

.cursor-dot {
  position: fixed;
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  background: white;
  border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none;
  mix-blend-mode: difference;
  z-index: 9999;
}

.cursor-outline {
  position: fixed;
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border: 1px solid white;
  border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none;
  mix-blend-mode: difference;
  z-index: 9998;
  transition: transform 0.15s ease-out;
}

.cursor-outline.hovering {
  transform: scale(1.5);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}
```

