## Quick Reference: Do vs Don't

| Avoid | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `rounded-lg` everywhere | Vary: `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-none`, custom |
| `shadow-md` | Custom shadows with color |
| `bg-blue-500` | Custom palette |
| System fonts | Character fonts (Space Grotesk, Outfit) |
| Centered everything | Asymmetric, offset layouts |
| 3-column feature grid | Bento grid, masonry |
| Generic hover states | Magnetic, 3D transforms |
| Static elements | Micro-interactions |
